cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.DL, cs.LG

This paper discusses the optimization of native-XML database management systems for decision-support applications, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also proposes a new join index for XML data warehouses, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and data structures (cs.DS). The experimental results and efficiency analysis involve machine learning (cs.LG) and deep learning (cs.DL) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DB, followed by cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.DL, and cs.LG.
